Get ready for some sizzling surprises and heart-pounding drama! Uorfi Javed has just dropped a bombshell on the Ex-Isle crew by bringing Ishita into the mix. Sparks fly and tensions rise as Digvijay and Unnati's budding connection faces a tsunami of challenges. Can they find harmony, or will jealousy ignite a fiery showdown?

But wait, the drama doesn't stop there! Over in Splitsvilla, Sunny Leone and Tanuj Virwani are stirring up trouble with their latest task, 'Flush Your Secrets.' It's a battle of wits and wills as contestants go head-to-head in a showdown of secrets. Winner takes all, while losers face the terrifying prospect of their deepest secrets being exposed to the world!

Get your popcorn ready and buckle up for a rollercoaster ride of emotions and revelations. Will love conquer all, or will chaos reign supreme? Tune in to the full episode to uncover the juicy truth!
